    "Rosenberg began a series of college visiting lectureships, the first at the New School of Social Research, 1953-1954.": [],
    "In 1956 the philosopher Maurice Merleau-Ponty asked Rosenberg to contribute the chapter on Marx for his <em>Les Philosophes C\u00e9l\u00e8bres</em>.": [
